A lesson at school, the topic of the lesson is Solving problems for the development of logical thinking. The teacher asks:
- What happens if an all-destructive core crashes into an indestructible wall?
Vovochka:
- Vodka will rise in price!
Mary Ivanovna:
- Why is that?
Vovochka:
- And dad always says that in our country, if some incomprehensible stuff happens, then vodka immediately becomes more expensive!
